{"text_id":23916,"tokens":["How"," to"," Account"," for"," Cost"," of"," Goods"," Sold","\n","Acc","ur","ately"," calculating"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," sold"," (","CO","GS",")"," is"," essential"," for"," running"," a"," successful"," business","."," To"," do"," this",","," you"," must"," be"," able"," to"," determine"," the"," value"," of"," the"," beginning"," inventory",","," account"," for"," any"," purchases",","," manufacturing"," costs",","," and"," labor"," costs",","," and"," establish"," the"," ending"," inventory","."," With"," this"," information",","," you"," can"," proceed"," to"," calculate"," the"," CO","GS"," with"," a"," periodic"," or"," perpetual"," inventory"," system","."," This"," article"," will"," explain"," how"," to"," account"," for"," cost"," of"," goods"," sold"," with"," FIFO",","," L","IFO",","," and"," average"," cost"," methods",".","\n","Determine"," the"," beginning"," inventory"," value","."," This"," should"," always"," be"," the"," ending"," inventory"," value"," from"," the"," previous"," reporting"," period","."," This"," value"," is"," used"," to"," calculate"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available",","," which"," will"," be"," compared"," to"," the"," current"," ending"," inventory"," in"," order"," to"," calculate"," the"," CO","GS",".","\n","Add"," the"," value"," of"," all"," inventory"," purchases","."," This"," includes"," any"," raw"," materials",","," manufacturing"," costs",","," and"," labor"," costs"," necessary"," for"," the"," production"," of"," the"," goods","."," These"," costs"," should"," be"," added"," to"," the"," beginning"," inventory"," value"," to"," calculate"," the"," total"," cost"," of"," goods"," available",".","\n","Calculate"," the"," labor"," costs"," involved"," for"," manufacturing"," the"," goods","."," This"," includes"," both"," direct"," labor"," costs"," (","those"," necessary"," to"," manufacture"," the"," goods",")"," and"," indirect"," labor"," costs"," (","those"," necessary"," to"," run"," the"," administrative"," and"," management"," functions"," within"," the"," business",")."," This"," amount"," should"," be"," added"," to"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available"," to"," get"," a"," complete"," sum"," of"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available",".","\n","Account"," for"," materials",","," supplies",","," and"," other"," costs"," of"," manufacturing","."," This"," includes"," costs"," such"," as"," packaging"," materials",","," advertising",","," shipping",","," machinery",","," and"," any"," other"," expenses"," related"," to"," the"," manufacturing"," of"," the"," goods","."," Once"," all"," of"," the"," material"," and"," labor"," costs"," have"," been"," accounted"," for",","," you"," will"," have"," a"," full"," sum"," of"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available",".","\n","Calculate"," the"," Cost"," of"," Goods"," Available","."," This"," is"," done"," by"," adding"," the"," beginning"," inventory"," value"," and"," all"," inventory"," purchases",","," materials",","," and"," related"," costs","."," This"," value"," is"," then"," compared"," to"," the"," current"," ending"," inventory"," to"," determine"," the"," CO","GS",".","\n","Choose"," from"," two"," methods"," to"," estimate"," the"," ending"," inventory","."," The"," first"," method"," is"," the"," gross"," profit"," method"," in"," which"," the"," CO","GS"," is"," estimated"," by"," subtracting"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available"," from"," the"," current"," revenues"," reported"," in"," the"," profit"," and"," loss"," statement","."," The"," second"," method"," is"," the"," retail"," inventory"," method"," in"," which"," the"," current"," cost"," structure"," of"," the"," goods"," is"," used"," to"," estimate"," the"," CO","GS",".","\n","Use"," the"," gross"," profit"," method"," to"," estimate"," ending"," inventory","."," This"," involves"," estimating"," the"," CO","GS"," by"," subtracting"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available"," from"," the"," total"," sales"," of"," the"," good"," in"," the"," profit"," and"," loss"," statement","."," This"," method"," is"," generally"," best"," when"," dealing"," with"," a"," wide"," variety"," of"," goods"," and"," multiple"," departments",".","\n","Use"," the"," retail"," inventory"," method"," to"," estimate"," ending"," inventory","."," This"," involves"," estimating"," the"," CO","GS"," based"," on"," the"," gross"," margin"," of"," the"," product","."," This"," method"," is"," useful"," when"," dealing"," with"," a"," more"," homogeneous"," line"," of"," goods"," with"," a"," consistent"," cost"," structure"," across"," the"," board",".","\n","Obtain"," an"," accurate"," ending"," inventory"," valuation"," periodically"," with"," a"," physical"," count"," or"," cycle"," count","."," This"," will"," provide"," the"," most"," up","-","to","-","date"," values"," for"," the"," ending"," inventory"," and"," ensure"," that"," the"," CO","GS"," is"," accurate",".","\n","Calculate"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," sold"," (","CO","GS",")"," if"," using"," a"," periodic"," inventory"," method","."," To"," do"," this",","," subtract"," the"," ending"," inventory"," value"," from"," the"," cost"," of"," goods"," available","."," This"," will"," provide"," the"," total"," value"," of"," the"," CO","GS",".","\n","Calculate"," the"," CO","GS"," if"," using"," a"," perpetual"," inventory"," method","."," If"," you"," are"," using"," a"," perpetual"," inventory"," system",","," the"," CO","GS"," can"," be"," calculated"," by"," subtracting"," the"," total"," purchases"," during"," the"," reporting"," period"," from"," the"," value"," of"," the"," goods"," sold"," during"," the"," same"," period",".","\n","Calculate"," CO","GS"," using"," the"," FIFO"," method","."," This"," method"," involves"," determining"," the"," cost"," of"," the"," oldest"," inventory"," first","."," For"," example",","," if"," you"," purchased"," an"," item"," for"," $","1","0"," three"," times"," during"," the"," period",","," and"," the"," value"," of"," the"," item"," rose"," each"," time"," you"," purchased"," it",","," the"," total"," CO","GS"," would"," be"," $","3","0"," for"," the"," three"," items",","," accounting"," for"," the"," oldest"," cost"," first",".","\n","Calculate"," CO","GS"," using"," L","IFO","."," This"," method"," involves"," calculating"," the"," CO","GS"," by"," accounting"," for"," the"," cost"," of"," the"," most"," recent"," purchase"," first","."," For"," example",","," again",","," if"," you"," purchased"," an"," item"," for"," $","1","0"," three"," times"," during"," the"," period",","," and"," the"," value"," of"," the"," item"," rose"," each"," time"," you"," purchased"," it",","," the"," total"," CO","GS"," calculated"," with"," the"," L","IFO"," method"," would"," be"," $","3","0"," for"," the"," three"," items",","," accounting"," for"," the"," most"," recent"," cost"," first",".","\n","Calculate"," CO","GS"," using"," the"," Average"," Cost"," method","."," This"," method"," involves"," calculating"," the"," CO","GS"," by"," taking"," the"," average"," of"," the"," cost"," of"," all"," the"," goods"," purchased","."," For"," example",","," if"," you"," purchased"," an"," item"," for"," $","1","0"," three"," times"," during"," the"," period",","," and"," the"," value"," of"," the"," item"," rose"," each"," time"," you"," purchased"," it",","," the"," total"," CO","GS"," would"," be"," $","2","2"," for"," the"," three"," items",","," calculating"," the"," average"," cost"," of"," $","7",".","3","3"," per"," item",".","\n","Record"," the"," journal"," entry"," if"," you"," are"," using"," a"," periodic"," inventory"," method","."," The"," entry"," should"," include"," the"," value"," of"," the"," ending"," inventory"," and"," the"," value"," of"," the"," CO","GS","."," The"," CO","GS"," will"," be"," de","bited"," from"," the"," inventory"," account",","," and"," the"," ending"," inventory"," will"," be"," credited"," to"," the"